Chain (Chantawit Tanasaewe), a young projectionist, decides to join Yod's 
(Worakan Rojanawat) mission to illegally record a newly released horror movie. 
Chain falls asleep during the screening and wakes up to find that Yod has 
already disappeared and left his camera behind. Suddenly, the horror movie that 
they were watching in the cinema starts to happen to them in real life.
